title Offer Service

actor User
participant "R: Runtime" as Runtime
participant "ProducerBuilder<I, R>" as ProducerBuilder
participant "Producer<R>" as Producer
participant "OfferedProducer<R>" as OfferedProducer

User -> Runtime: producer_builder::<VehicleInterface>(\nInstanceSpecifier)
Runtime --> User: ProducerBuilder<I, R>

User -> ProducerBuilder: build()
ProducerBuilder --> User: Result<Producer<R>>

Note over Producer: Producer instance created

User -> Producer: offer()
Producer --> User: Result<OfferedProducer<R>>

Note over OfferedProducer: Service now discoverable\nby consumers via Runtime

User -> OfferedProducer: Access event publishers
OfferedProducer --> User: Publisher<T>

Note over User: Publishers ready for\nsending data samples

@enduml
